xmms (1.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging of XMMS Resurrection v1.3.0.
  * Migrated from GTK+2 to GTK3; CMake replaces Autotools as primary build.
  * Freedesktop icon set (7 sizes) and .desktop entry included.
  * Supports ALSA and PulseAudio output plugins.
  * Supports MP3 (mpg123), OGG Vorbis, FLAC, WAV, AIFF input plugins.

 -- Joel Hanger <joel@tacitsoft.dev>  Mon, 28 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000
